{"tid":832512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打正常樣既時候無問題 但笑起來真係好淫 好樣衰","createTime":"2018-09-22T19:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T17:52:54.000Z","uid":184570,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc4d9dc54ea57edc5f6c2f28ede154d56176af0","tid":832512,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"如題 小弟一直探討緊自己個樣邊度出左問題 <br />\n<br />\n點知岩岩發現原來自己唔笑既時候有中上樣 但一笑就即刻變得好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n身邊既朋友都話過我笑得好淫賤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟點樣先可以笑得好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心覺得其實笑都係一種學問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真Post 勿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8222d42a8d9a0a9189332e51d61f7209e7a60c25","tid":832512,"uid":181432,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/033339_ed74d398e379ef3e36b040b4ced97800.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F033339_ed74d398e379ef3e36b040b4ced97800.png&h=23e5f585&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e79310315faaaf878f552b337a218dd6d7f6b1c2","tid":832512,"uid":47147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90e7df18e4edc9ccd1fca5cb6719ebd3cd254b89","tid":832512,"uid":184570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8222d42a8d9a0a9189332e51d61f7209e7a60c25","tid":832512,"uid":181432,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/033339_ed74d398e379ef3e36b040b4ced97800.png\" data-